These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, metal
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of metal is not to the right of the fan of metal##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | metal | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, thriller
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard
1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | ferret | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, subway
1. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | roller | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | card-games |

 #################################

 
